DJ Dave Lee Travis faced a media scrum as he arrived at court to face 11 counts of indecent assault and one of sexual assault against nine alleged victims.

Arriving at Westminster Magistrates' Court, the 68-year-old, whose real name is David Patrick Griffin, refused to comment on the case against him.

He said: 'I'm not protesting anything, I've got nothing to say. I'd like to speak for three hours to everybody to tell you the story. I'm making no comment.'

